net.hudup.core

Class RegisterTableList

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.core.RegisterTableList

  • public class RegisterTableList
extends java.lang.Object
    This utility class represents a list of RegisterTable (s). Note that PluginStorage manages many RegisterTable (s) and each RegisterTable stores algorithms having the same type. For example, a register table manages recommendation algorithms (recommenders) whereas another manages metrics for evaluating recommenders. As a convention, RegisterTable is called register table and this class is called register table item list. Note that each register table in this class is wrapped by RegisterTableList.RegisterTableItem class called register table item.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
